02:21:22.656 --> 02:21:26.714
Just like a toddler falls, we, as babies in Christ, fall too.

02:21:26.715 --> 02:21:31.581
But we stand up again, and we run to God and say, 'God, I need you.'We don't run from him.

02:21:31.582 --> 02:21:35.961
The devil will be immediately there to say, 'I told you you weren't saved.

02:21:35.962 --> 02:21:42.803
I told you you were not right. A real Christian wouldn't do what you just did.'But he's a liar.

02:21:42.804 --> 02:21:47.440
He's the accuser of the brethren. He's always out there trying to tempt you.

02:21:47.441 --> 02:21:55.104
He'll mess you up, and then he'll hit you in the head with it. He is a piece of trash.

02:21:55.105 --> 02:22:03.412
But I believe that our sin is none of the devil's business. It's the Lord's. 'Lord, I need you. I need you. Shut the doors.

02:22:03.413 --> 02:22:09.059
Thank you, Lord, for helping me.'So, we're so excited you're here tonight. We love you.

02:22:09.060 --> 02:22:16.645
We're excited about all 59 of you who gave your heart to Jesus Christ tonight. Welcome to the family.

02:22:16.646 --> 02:22:22.050
All 59 people who just accepted the Lord Jesus Christ tonight, welcome to the family.

02:22:22.051 --> 02:22:31.919
We're so excited you're here. Stay around us, pray with us, and I believe you're part of the end-time army.

02:22:31.920 --> 02:22:37.565
God has a plan for you, and I'm so excited that you sold your heart to Jesus.

02:22:37.566 --> 02:22:40.083
You're selling out to Jesus tonight. You gave your heart to Jesus.

02:22:40.084 --> 02:22:46.399
You're saying, 'I need you.'You recognize that you need a Lord and Savior. So, praise the Lord.

02:22:46.400 --> 02:22:51.711
Well, to the rest of you who came out tonight, thank you for praying with us.

02:22:51.712 --> 02:23:01.613
We have much work to do from what I just saw. But I'll leave you with that. It's getting late again, and we will pray again.

02:23:01.614 --> 02:23:12.199
Like I said, when I get in that river, what I saw tonight was a little like, wow, things that I did not even say.

02:23:12.200 --> 02:23:17.239
