02:23:17.240 --> 02:23:20.599
I don't want to just say certain things anymore on the internet.

02:23:20.600 --> 02:23:26.119
I have to really watch some of this stuff. Some of this was very, very bad.

02:23:26.120 --> 02:23:31.157
And so, I'll have to talk to who I need to talk to about it first.

02:23:31.158 --> 02:23:36.746
God bless you all, and we love you. We love every single one of you.

02:23:36.747 --> 02:23:43.994
